Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここだったか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所で寝ていると\N熱中症になるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep lying there, you'll get heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:55.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんただって ラボの屋上で\N寝っ転がってたでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You sleep on the roof of the lab \Nall the time, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:57.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに 今は曇ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's cloudy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:59.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりには会えたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橋田が コミマでは\N会えなかったみたいって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashida said he couldn't find her at Comima...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ その後 会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I met up with her after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:14.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:16.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:31.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい… 雨だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:33.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわあ～！\Nああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:39.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんぞ これ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,WTF?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:43.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:47.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少し 早く忠告してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you warn me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:50.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかげで 下着まで\Nびしょぬれじゃない もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm soaked, down to my underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと 声は かけた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I did tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いていなかったのは\Nクリスティーナの…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault, Christina, for not listen—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:56.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ… このHENTAI！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に 見ようと思って\N見たわけではないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:07.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様が そんな透けやすい服を\N着ているのが…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's your fault for wearing such thin clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたが HENTAIだってこと\N忘れてたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten you were such a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:13.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の貧相なヌードなど\N見るに値するとでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd want to see your stick figure in the nude...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上 言ったら\Nあんたの大脳新皮質を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One more word, and I turn \Nyour neocortex into a flower pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:17.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ポン酢漬けにしてやるから！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:20.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう脅し…\N近づかないで！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of threat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って 何それ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:26.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を捜している時\Nどこかに引っかけたか…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I got scratched somewhere, \Nwhen I was looking for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… ドジっ子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:30.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の属性は\Nマッドサイエンティストであり…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm classified as a "mad scientist"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:33.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はいはい\Nまったく 世話が焼けるわね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:36.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貸して ちょうど\Nソーイングセットがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand that over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a sewing kit on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,縫ってあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fix it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ソーイングセット？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A sewing kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:43.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでも 相対的に見れば\N家庭的なほうなのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider myself more family-oriented
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,than most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら 脱いで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先に言っておくけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:52.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この暗さだから\N出来については期待しないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's dark, so don't expect too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:56.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと 糸が何色になるか\N出てからの お楽しみね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can look forward to finding out, \Nafter we leave, what color thread I used.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:04:00.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒 赤 ピンク 確率は３分の１
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Black, red, pink...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a 33% chance of each one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ…\Nピンクが出ないよう 祈ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just pray it isn't pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:04.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ… 来ないでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:07.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろ\Nお前の貧相なヌードに興味など…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in that stick figure of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:10.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ポン酢漬けにするって\N言ってんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you... A flower pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:13.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ… まったく…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:17.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこをぶらついたら\Nこんな所 破けるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you have to go, \Nto rip your clothes like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:20.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は ラボに行って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I went to the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:23.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ランドリー 散歩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the laundry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:27.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから\Nお前が泊まっているホテル
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then to your hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホテル？ 行ったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The hotel? You stopped by?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のせいだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:35.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メールの返信は よこさない\N電話にも出ない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't answer my messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't picking up your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか 心配してくれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you worried about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:42.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助手の管理は ラボのあるじである\N俺の仕事だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As head of the lab, \Nit's my job to keep track of my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:48.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ できないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ！\Nうわっ… あっ 冷たっ！ お前！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cold. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く着なさい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in the stick figure \Nof a nude mad scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マッドサイエンティストの\N貧相なヌードなど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:05:00.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,興味ないのだからな\Nワ～ッハッハッハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:10.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分 この近くよね\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:17.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が… 刺された場所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The place I was stabbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:22.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ… どうして それを？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:25.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり 夢にしては
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain and despair were too real for a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:29.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,痛さや絶望感が\Nあまりにリアルだったから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:32.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紅莉栖 まさか お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu. You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:36.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん 私の中にもね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have hazy memories inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぼんやりと記憶があるの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,淡い まるで 幻みたいな記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Weak, almost nonexistent memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,刺された時のことだけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just of being stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:51.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部のことも ぼんやりと覚えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you, too... hazily...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:55.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりを助けようと必死になって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How desperate you were to save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:06:00.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人で傷つきながらも\N前に進もうとしているの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How you kept pressing forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,even hurt and all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:03.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して 元の世界には戻せないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't made it back to your original world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも 必死に あらがって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've kept going,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:10.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりの名前を必死で叫んで\N涙を流して
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,kept calling her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,kept crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:14.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひたむきに助けようとしている\N岡部がいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kept trying to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:19.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その顔を見る度に 私は思うの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see that face,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think about how important she is to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:24.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部にとって どれだけ\Nまゆりが かけがえのない存在か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And about whether it's possible for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:30.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かが誰かを\Nここまで大切に思えるのかって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to truly care for another person that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:36.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 私は 岡部に協力したい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部の手助けをしたいと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:48.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 岡部 まゆりを助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe, save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:55.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部は\Nまゆりを助けるべきなのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You must save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は どうなる？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go to the beta world line, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:07:02.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,β世界線に行ったら 死ぬんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:08.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そうするしかないの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:10.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたが\N一番 よく分かってるでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that better than anyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,選択肢は １つしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:16.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を… 見捨てろっていうのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me to abandon you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他に方法がある？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there another way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日から何度も考えた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about the following since yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までみたいに 何か打つ手が…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Isn't there some other way?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か方法があるんじゃないかって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Isn't there something else we can do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 無理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, I can't come up with anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:35.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度ばかりは どうしようもない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Except going to the beta world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:39.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,β世界線に行くしか方法はないの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:51.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなの… 俺は認めない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to accept this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めない！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:58.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できるわけないだろ\N紅莉栖を見捨てるなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't abandon Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:01.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつを見殺しにして\N生きていくなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let her die and then keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:04.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことに 何の意味がある？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would the point of that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:08.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は… 俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:13.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ…！\Nあっ… はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:17.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ はあ はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:25.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げたって…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run away, but that'll just make it worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:29.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げたって 苦しくなるだけよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:37.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度 タイムリープしたって\N１％の壁は越えられない！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you time leap,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't get past the 1% barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やってみなきゃ分からないだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know until we try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:44.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが死ぬところを\N見るだけなのよ？ 何回も…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just see Mayuri die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの 岡部が壊れちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壊れなど… しない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:54.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が 何回\Nまゆりの死を見てきたと思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do you think I've watched her die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:57.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何回も見てきた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:09:02.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何回も 何回も 何回も 何回も…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And again and again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう そんなもので\N心が壊れたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't destroy me... \NThe number of times I see it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度 繰り返そうが同じ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が\N何 言ってるか 分かってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:18.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが 苦しんで死んでいくのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri's going to suffer and die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:21.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢そんなもの｣なわけないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say it doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:24.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで 岡部の心が\N動かないんだとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If that doesn't affect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 岡部の心は壊れている…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then your heart's already broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に壊れちゃうよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it really will break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってる 気付いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed it long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:44.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが何度も死んでいるのに\N俺は驚かなくなっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times Mayuri died, \NI stopped being surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:48.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつの間にか 心がマヒしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd gone numb without even knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが死ぬ時刻を確かめようと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I even waited before time leaping, \Njust to see when she'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:54.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タイムリープせずに\N待っていたことすらあった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが死ぬのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it just stopped affecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の心は\Nいつからか動かなくなって…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:03.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冷静に やり直せばいいって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere inside, I was calmly telling myself \Nthat I could do it over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:07.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかで そう思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:16.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりを助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:20.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうしないと\N本当に 岡部が壊れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, it will destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:24.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりを見殺しになんかしたら\N絶対に後悔する！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let her die, you'll regret it... I'm certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:27.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりを助けようっていう\N思いだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I have come this far, \Nfrom the single wish to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部と私は ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:32.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで やめたら\N一生 後悔し続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stop, we'll always regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:36.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも まゆりを助けたら お前は…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戻るだけよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To the first world line, before the D-mail was sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:40.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｄメールが送られなかった\N最初の世界線に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:44.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが 私のためであり\N岡部のためでもある！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's best for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's what's best for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many times have we fought, \Nover these past twenty days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:56.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この20日間 何度も衝突した
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いに 憎まれ口をたたき合った
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've made fun of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相談し合ったりもした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've talked about our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When my back was against the wall, \NI turned to Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:05.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,追い詰められた俺が\N助けを求めたのは 紅莉栖だった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の話を黙って聞き\N信じてくれたのは 紅莉栖だった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kurisu was the one who listened to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who believed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:15.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,18歳で学術誌に論文が載った\N天才少女は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At eighteen, a genius with a \Npublished academic paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常に 冷静で 強がりで\Nプライドが高くて おせっかいで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always calm, always strong-willed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always so proud and nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,根は 真面目すぎるほど真面目で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But always so kind and honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:28.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は いつだって\N彼女の語る理論にしびれて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her theories continually amazed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:31.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女の言葉を胸に刻み込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I remembered everything she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:35.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女の動きを目で追っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watched everything she did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単なる仲間じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She wasn't just another lab member.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:42.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺とって 牧瀬 紅莉栖は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To me, Makise Kurisu was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:51.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:55.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を助けられない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:03.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:08.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のために\Nそこまで苦しんでくれて…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For suffering so much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:12.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで お前なんだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして お前なんだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:21.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 世界線が変わるって\Nどういうことなんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what does it mean to change world lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:25.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしかしたら\N岡部が β世界線に行った瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the second you go to the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:29.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界から 岡部という存在が\N消えるだけかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll just disappear from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:33.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別の岡部という存在に\N変わるのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you trade places with another Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:37.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの… 意味がない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:41.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことない 私は死んでない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm dead in the beta world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:44.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,β世界線の私が\N死んでいたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no guarantee that I'm going to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:47.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ここにいる私が死ぬ保証は\Nどこにもない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:51.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無数の世界線に\N別の私がいるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be another me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,amidst all the other, infinite world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その意思が つながって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And our minds are connected and comprise "me."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:56.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分という存在が\Nあるのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:13:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それって… ステキだと思わない？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that'd be wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be everywhere, in every time, at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:05.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あらゆる時 あらゆる場所に\N自分がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:08.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かを愛する強い気持ちが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A great love for someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かを信じる強い感情が
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a great belief in something,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a great desire to pass on something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:13.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かを伝えたいという強い思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:18.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時を超え つながって\N今の自分があるのだとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If all those things surpass time itself and create "you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:21.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは すばらしいこと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that be wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't think of it as abandoning me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:26.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから\N見殺しにするなんて思わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:31.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界線が変わっても\Nたった一人 岡部が忘れなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the world line changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you don't forget me, I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は そこにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:35.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のことは 絶対に忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the person I care for most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰よりも大切な人のことを\N忘れたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それって…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事実だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How... It's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと なんで 急に…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:56.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は お前が好きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は どうなんだ？\Nと 言いますと？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:02.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いておきたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:06.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は 俺のことを\Nどう思ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:11.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知りたいのか？\Nああ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔を… 目を閉じろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face... Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:18.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？\Nいいから 閉じなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,べ 別に\Nしたくてしたわけじゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't want to do that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:55.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ ファーストキスのような\N強烈な行為と共に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But experiences, such as your first kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:15:00.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海馬に記憶されたエピソードは\N忘却されにくいのよ だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that are stored in the hippocampus with your \Nstrong memories are harder to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:05.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は\Nこれが ファーストキスではない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't my first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:07.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な 生意気な童貞のくせに！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You bratty virgin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるさい 処女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとも ファーストキスは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My first kiss wasn't at all romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:14.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ロマンチックなものでは\Nなかったがな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:18.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく\N今のは 印象としては弱い
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That last one only left a weak impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度だ\Nえっ？ あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to forget, not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:25.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に忘れたくないから\N念には念を入れる いいな？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll take extra care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:28.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなら しょうがないな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a kiss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:30.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キスだけだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間が\Nあっという間に流れていく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time is passing so quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今だけは アインシュタインに\N文句を言いたい気分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, I feel like complaining to Einstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whether time is slow or fast
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間は 人の意識によって\N長くなったり短くなったりする
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}depends on perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relativity theory is so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:57.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相対性理論って\Nとてもロマンチックで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:16:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても切ないものだね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure about not saying it to Mayuri and Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:12.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりとダルは\N本当に いいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone seeing me off would just make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:15.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなに見送られると\Nつらくなるから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's only you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:20.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部だけなら\N何のためらいもなく日本をたてる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can leave Japan without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジョークよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手土産だ 受け取れ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:27.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:29.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いらねえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I upgraded it to version 2.67.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:32.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バージョン2.67に\Nアップデートしてある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:37.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ややこしいわね\Nでも まあ 受け取っておく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll take it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:40.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:48.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紅莉栖！\Nそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お返し！ ふっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you throwing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこに投げている\Nちゃんと受け取れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:17.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure, whatever happens, you're going to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:33.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから きっと\N岡部は つらい思いをする
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only you will remember me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:36.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のことを\N誰も覚えていない世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in a world where no one else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:40.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ一人 私を覚えているなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間を\Nなにより大事にする岡部には
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More than anyone else, you care for your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that'll be painful for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つらいことだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:51.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:55.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 私には\Nそのつらさが いとおしい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But somehow, I'm glad you'll have that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラボにいる何気ない時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those times when you're sitting around the lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you drink a can of juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:02.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジュースを口にした時\N街を歩く その一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you walk around town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:07.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつか 誰かとキスした時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And someday, when you kiss someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:11.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもじゃなくてもいい\N100回に１回でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't have to be every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can be one time out of a hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私を思い出してほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'd like you to remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:17.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに 私はいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I'll be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１％の壁の向こうに\N私は 必ず いるから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be there, beyond the 1% barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部 岡部…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっと！ オカリン 見つけた！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジで あったぞ これっしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is totally it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If we delete this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを消せば…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ミッション コンプリート？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:53.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン 大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:19:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これより 現在を司る女神作戦\N最終フェイズを開始する！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We now begin the final phase of Operation Verdandi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our victory is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝利の時は来た！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have overcome all conspiracies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:06.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あらゆる陰謀に屈せず 己の…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:09.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,己の信念を貫き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Upholding our ideals to the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, we have fought through \Nthe battle of Ragnarok!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:13.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々は ついに\Nラグナロックを戦い抜いたのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝利のために
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank those who have worked so hard for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が手足となって戦ってくれた\N仲間たちに感謝を！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to ensure this victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful to all those I have had to sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:24.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,犠牲となった すべての思いに\N感謝を…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:29.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,訪れるのは 俺が望んだ世界であり
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What comes now is the world I wished for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all the choice of Steins Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:32.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ては 運命石の扉の選択である！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界は…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:40.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再構築される！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be rebuilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kurisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紅莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまない…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部！\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:55.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ はあ はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部 私も…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:20:00.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紅莉栖！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:19:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:03.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も 岡部のことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:12.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆり\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Lab Member 004?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラボメンNo.004は誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,004?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,004？ う～ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't an 004.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:29.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,004の人はいないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:35.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… フフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the battle of Ragnarok has ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ここに\Nラグナロックの勝敗は決した！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I, the mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma, \Nhave controlled time itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:42.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この俺 狂気の\Nマッドサイエンティストである
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鳳凰院 凶真は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,foiling the Organization and SERN's schemes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:47.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,機関 および\NＳＥＲＮのあらゆる攻撃に対し
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and bringing about complete victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時空を操ることで\N完全に勝利したのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:56.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界の支配構造はリセットされ\N混沌の未来が待つであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's ruling structure has been reset!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And a future of chaos awaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the choice of Steins Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:21:00.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これこそが 運命石の扉の選択！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン もういいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:07.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を？\N俺は 今 華麗なる勝利宣言を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just issued a declaration of victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:11.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう その口調を\N続けなくてもいいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to talk like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:15.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは もう大丈夫だから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can cry for yourself, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:19.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンは オカリンのために\N泣いてもいいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We no longer need the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電話レンジは もう要らない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:30.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このマシンがあったことで\N紅莉栖と出会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of it, I met Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:34.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けれど このマシンがあったことで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But because of it, so many were hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:38.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たくさんの人が傷ついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鳳凰院 凶真が死んだように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as Hououin Kyouma has died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Phone Microwave should die, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:44.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電話レンジも また\N死ぬべきなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きることは 本来\Nやり直しが利かないことだから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Living should mean no do-overs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:53.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで いいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is for the best. Right, Kurisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:56.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだよな？ 紅莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:02.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は～い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:01.27,Default - margin,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:04.02,Default - margin,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nだ 誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:09.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,父さん？ 何？ オカリン？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin, there's a mysterious girl \Nwho wants to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.16,0:23:12.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン 謎の女が代われってさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:14.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come to the Radio Building's roof immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い！\N今すぐ ラジ館屋上に来て！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:18.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？ お前は？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come from the year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.15,0:23:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしは 2036年から来た\N橋田 至の娘 阿万音 鈴羽！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hashida Itaru's daughter, Amane Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:29.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鈴羽…？ ちょっと待て！\N鈴羽が なんで ここにいるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe what I'm about to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い あたしの言うことを信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You must stop World War III.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:34.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第三次世界大戦を防ぐために
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.15,0:29:45.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理美さんの友人の\N古葉詩織と申します
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.12,0:29:48.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの 理美は今 ちょ…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.13,0:29:51.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弁護士をしております
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.13,0:29:56.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は\N理美さんの友人としてではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.13,0:29:58.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代理人として来ました
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.12,0:30:01.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代理人…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.12,0:30:04.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チューリップです
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.12,0:30:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,公園 通過
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.13,0:30:09.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単刀直入に申し上げます
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.13,0:30:13.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悠斗君を理美さんに\N引き渡していただきたいんです
